{"tid":1602710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果依場運動輸左 我地點對得住自己","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:58:40.000Z","uid":122021,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b5f49b8e2257678f418732696493ca1340f3d8","tid":1602710,"uid":122021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"三個月 義士死亡 好多人下落不明<br />\n新屋嶺發生乜事 冇人知<br />\n最近死因可疑人數不段上升 未能沉冤得雪<br />\n女義士爆眼、太古近距離掃射、721、831⋯⋯ 歷歷在目<br />\n黑警行動越來越過份<br />\n五大訴求 淨係施捨一樣<br />\n<br />\n由之前兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不篤灰 不割蓆 不分化<br />\n到宜家互相猜疑<br />\n<br />\n一首肥媽歌 何妖改詞 可以瘋狂玩膠<br />\n真普選 重組警隊 獨立調查 彷彿拋諸腦後<br />\n<br />\n希望大家玩夠 可以重新對準政權<br />\n唔可以令到義士死得不明不白<br />\n唔可以令到無辜傷者追究無門<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n十月一 賀佢老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"18e039cc9f8171f2e7306c3467e73607887a13c9","tid":1602710,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a64ad2a81556936c82e058f1fa64a049d021d90","tid":1602710,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f70c0afcb38e22af0084f1e95890da0669163e1","tid":1602710,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7251a3caad12476c5425dd151a6faec43a6c8ae3","tid":1602710,"uid":122021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eea7f618e2558ec575997f5950ea27459e9ec64","tid":1602710,"uid":122021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865ad39dbde07c13171f6768eab45777a2e42a30","tid":1602710,"uid":122021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:25:48.000Z","msg"